{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01LMfyhDFPeEDq7Ti6XKan5d","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The finding is a fabrication issue: the label \"レスポンスヘッダのカスタマイズ不可\" (customization impossible) should be \"レスポンスヘッダのカスタマイズが容易でない\" or similar to match the source \"容易にカスタマイズ出来ない\" (cannot easily customize).\n\nI need to fix constraint 2's label from \"カスタマイズ不可\" to reflect \"容易にカスタマイズ出来ない\".","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":12430,"cache_read_input_tokens":18408,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":12430,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"beae6992-9137-43b3-8c17-b89a1c232eea","uuid":"43b8cd81-6baa-4239-995e-153f7dcbbbdc"}
